During a press briefing aboard Air Force One, White House Deputy Press Secretary Raj Shah discussed several topics including the President's upcoming remarks on the tax cut bill, the President's frustration with media coverage on his immigration views, the possibility of a government shutdown, the President's evolving stance on immigration, and the ongoing investigation by Special Counsel Robert Mueller. Shah also addressed questions about the President's alleged affair with Stephanie Clifford, also known as Stormy Daniels, and the President's stance on North Korea and Russia.